rows.Name: Appetizers
rows.Description: Small dishes served before the main course to stimulate the appetite.

rows.Name: Main Course
rows.Description: Hearty and satisfying main dishes, including meat, poultry, seafood, and vegetarian options.

rows.Name: Pizza
rows.Description: Delicious Italian dish consisting of a yeasted flatbread typically topped with tomato sauce and cheese and baked in an oven.

rows.Name: Pasta
rows.Description: Traditional Italian dish made from dough of durum wheat flour and water, typically served with sauce or other toppings.

rows.Name: Burger
rows.Description: Classic American dish consisting of a grilled or fried patty of ground meat, usually beef, served in a sliced bun.

rows.Name: Salads
rows.Description: Fresh and healthy salads made with vegetables, fruits, and dressings.

rows.Name: Soups
rows.Description: Warm and comforting soups made with various ingredients.

rows.Name: Desserts
rows.Description: Sweet treats and confections enjoyed after the main meal.

rows.Name: Sandwiches
rows.Description: A food typically consisting of vegetables, sliced cheese or meat, placed on or between slices of bread.

rows.Name: Seafood
rows.Description: Delicious dishes made from various types of seafood such as fish, shrimp, crab, and lobster.

rows.Name: Caprese Salad
rows.Description: A classic Italian salad made with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, basil leaves, olive oil, and balsamic vinegar

rows.Name: Stuffed Mushrooms
rows.Description: Mushrooms filled with a savory mixture of breadcrumbs, cheese, herbs, and sometimes sausage, baked until golden brown

rows.Name: Bruschetta
rows.Description: Grilled bread topped with diced tomatoes, garlic, basil, olive oil, and sometimes other ingredients like balsamic glaze or cheese

rows.Name: Spinach and Artichoke Dip
rows.Description: A creamy dip made with spinach, artichokes, cheese, and various seasonings, often served warm with tortilla chips or bread for dipping

rows.Name: Shrimp Cocktail
rows.Description: Chilled shrimp served with a tangy cocktail sauce made from ketchup, horseradish, lemon juice, Worcestershire sauce, and other seasonings
